    "E \"The patient presents with symptoms of rickettsial smallpox due to infection with Rickettsia akari, including fever, rash, and severely itchy patches.",
    "The diagnosis was made by physical examination and blood tests.",
    "Main symptoms: fever, rash, itchy spots\"In this example we observe that the corresponding ICD (A79.1 Rickettsienpocken durch Rickettsia akari) is not directly mentioned in the text and is therefore difficult to annotate.",
